{"tid":2413251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【 武漢肺炎後遺症】 近兩成男康復者精液完全無精子","createTime":"2021-02-18T14:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T02:36:29.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"19c7d6591dcad6a29e0702962eea700773a970c4","tid":2413251,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://file.youlai.cn/cnkfile1/M00/13/B0/oYYBAFo7c1KAEhv2AAIgHxjVPCM71.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile.youlai.cn%2Fcnkfile1%2FM00%2F13%2FB0%2FoYYBAFo7c1KAEhv2AAIgHxjVPCM71.jpeg&h=1067c5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少新冠肺炎患者即使康復後，仍出現後遺症，情況因人而異。意大利佛羅倫斯大學一項近期研究發現，在一批新冠肺炎男性康復者當中，兩成五人的精子數量偏低，近兩成人的精液中更完全沒有精子，亦即可能導致不育。研究亦引伸，症狀較嚴重的患者較可能出現無精子情況。<br />\n<br />\n研究分析了43位新冠肺炎男性康復者，年齡介乎30歲至65歲，當中11人的精子數量偏低，8人患上「無精子症」。這些研究對象本身育有子女，意味著具有生育能力。<br />\n<br />\n研究報告於本月已在醫學期刊《Human Reproduction》發表，並指出影響精子數量的因素包括用作治療的抗病毒藥物、抗生素及類固醇等等。 <br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Live Science"},{"pid":"6030d0898471b506c81fe27af5b7157f636ef959","tid":2413251,"uid":21141,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"可以免手術閹割<br />\n無限中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9619d413de908b62aebda59ac9d82b1cc1b6f35f","tid":2413251,"uid":362766,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:34:14.000Z","msg":"屌你咩，連呢啲都有圖<br />\n就算落圖都落張cream pie啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8ee842ced5b40dda92ad2f832600a4f48fe935","tid":2413251,"uid":353080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:35:14.000Z","msg":"好想吞"},{"pid":"24d197037370121c7ba2bd1de1112ba06087ca89","tid":2413251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces